*Osoba* je zaista zanimljiva. (The person is really interesting.)
Moguće je da će *osoba* biti spremna za sutra. (It is possible that the person will be ready for tomorrow.)
Jedna *osoba* može da menja život drugima. (One person can change the lives of others.)
Ona je bila izuzetna *osoba*. (She was an exceptional person.)
Oni su bili očajni da pronađu *osobu* koja će im pomoći. (They were desperate to find a person who would help them.)
Mnogi veruju da *osoba* ima dušu. (Many believe that a person has a soul.)